tArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>자녀들 초등학교가 봄 단기방학을 실시합니다. <br></span><span>학교도 못가고 심심해할 애들을 위해 엄마는 여행을 기획합니다. <br></span><span><br></span><span>아빠 빼고!<br></span><span>...<br></span><span><br></span><span>여행을 떠나면서 하는 말이<br></span><span>'냉장고에 닭 있으니 요리해서 먹어요. <span>(당신이 안먹으면 냉동칸으로 옮겨야 할 것 같아)</span>'<br></span><span><br></span><span>타의에 의해 잠시 독거남이 된 아빠는 (타의에 의해) 요리에 도전하기로 합니다. <br></span><span><br></span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1493635771498-715754941_image_0_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/42e3da61e72da452.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\",\"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1493635771498-715754941_image_0_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/42e3da61e72da452.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/42e3da61e72da452.jpg\" data-width=\"720\" data-height=\"960\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\" data-attachment-id=\"IdvOxM2baewRR_2H9T9wTFmMk-OA\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span><span>(네*버에서 검색해서 첫번째에 뜬 어느 블로거가 시키는데로)</span><br></span><span>생닭을 물로 씻어서 채에 받쳐둡니다. <br></span><span><br></span><span><span>별로 먹음직 스럽지 않은 생닭의 비주얼이여!</span><br></span><span>혼자 먹을 건데, 많기도 하여라. <br></span><span><br></span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1493635771498-715754941_image_1_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e6677ed64458bba0.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\",\"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1493635771498-715754941_image_1_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e6677ed64458bba0.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e6677ed64458bba0.jpg\" data-width=\"720\" data-height=\"960\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\" data-attachment-id=\"I6LEllh0yqsDWEP5ge5vLGdW9Qpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>야채를 준비합니다. <br></span><span>이런......<br></span><span>닭볶음탕의 핵심인 '감자'가 없습니다. <br></span><span>허탈하지만, 귀찮습니다. <br></span><span>누구 줄 것도 아니고, 내가 먹을거니까. <br></span><span>그냥 이대로 진행합니다</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1493635771498-715754941_image_2_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf59ad3cbcc82680.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\",\"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1493635771498-715754941_image_2_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf59ad3cbcc82680.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf59ad3cbcc82680.jpg\" data-width=\"720\" data-height=\"960\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\" data-attachment-id=\"IT6Zfn3WgsoIJ-n9QJTcPBnXlJDY\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                      